<SLUG> BC-ANGLO-SAXON-RETURN-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE ANGLO-SAXONS ARE BACK  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary, Humor Editors)   (ATTN. EDITORS: The following 550-word material from The New York
Times Syndicate is for use by clients of The Economist.
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
For purchase information, call 1-888-269-8796, or Debra Weydert at
732-390-4480.)  
