   &UR; INTERNATIONAL &LR;  (``i'' code)
</P>
<P>
   SIERRA-LEONE-U.N. (United Nations) _ Developments in Sierra
Leone, where more than 90 U.N. workers have been captured by rebels
from the Revolutionary United Front. By Christopher S. Wren.
</P>
<P>
   With
</P>
<P>
   SIERRA-LEONE-U.S. (Washington) _ The Clinton administration
appears uncertain about what action to take in Sierra Leone. By
Jane Perlez.
