<P>
   RAC-DERBY-ADVANCE (Louisville, Ky.) _ How Fusaichi Pegasus will
do in the paddock, or on the way to the gate before the Derby
throng, which numbered 151,051, last year, remains to be seen. By
Ron Indrisano. 950 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
