like Chrysler's PT and the Toyota MR2 Spyder sports car, the
eminently practical Honda Odyssey minivan and luxury vehicles like
BMW's X5 sport utility and Mercedes' flagship S-Class lineup.
Orders go on waiting lists and languish unfilled for months. By
Micheline Maynard.
